情 | publisher=国际在线 | accessdate=2014-05-22 | language=zh-hans | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140522071302/http://gb.cri.cn/42071/2014/05/22/6071s4550755.htm | archive-date=2014-05-22 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

